205.1	Mark_Cuban	Mark Cuban	Mark Cuban (born July 31, 1958) is an American business magnate and investor with a background in the computing and software industries. He is the owner of the National Basketball Association's Dallas Mavericks, Landmark Theatres, and Magnolia Pictures, and the chairman of the HDTV cable network HDNet. He is also a "shark" investor on the television series Shark Tank. In 2011, Cuban wrote an e-book, How to Win at the Sport of Business, in which he chronicles his life experiences in business and sports.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3c/Mark_Cuban%2C_Web_2.0_Conference.jpg/220px-Mark_Cuban%2C_Web_2.0_Conference.jpg
